entries.title: My First Entry
entries.content: Today I'm feeling very pressured to make progress on my project, but at the same time very sleepy.

entries.title: My Second Entry
entries.content: It's unbelievable how much I've learned in the past 3 months. It doesn't feel like it at times, but just thinking about it makes me want to continue.

entries.title: My Third Entry
entries.content: Oh my god, the kitty has grown so much so fast. He is a full-sized cat now!

entries.title: I got DELETE working!
entries.content: I finally got the DELETE ENTRY functionality working! It feels GREAT!

entries.title: Destroyer Cat
entries.content: The cat scratched the leather chair, agh! I knew this would eventually happen, but it bothered me regardless. It is my favourite chair, and it was so expensive!

entries.title: I'm REALLY liking React
entries.content: I never thought I'd be so into a technology developed by Facebook - a social media I don't like at all. React, however, is pretty cool and I want to stick with it for now.

entries.title: Big Day Tomorrow
entries.content:
Tomorrow's the day I finish with my capstone project.

I can't believe time went by this fast, and how much I've learned in these short three months.

I'm a little sad that the program is ending - let's see what the future has in hand next.

entries.title: Back to Work
entries.content: First week back to work since the quarantine began. I was feeling lazy to go at first, but then realized I actually missed it.

entries.title: My Cat is Toxic
entries.content: One day, this cat will be the end of me.

entries.title: I Can Feel the Summer
entries.content: Even though it's been summer for some time now, the weather seems to neglect that fact. However, we've had three sunny days in a row now! The wind is still chilly, though.
